Bash(docker exec backend-postgres-1 psql -U postgres -d file_extension_blocker -c "
SELECT 
    s.space_id, 
    s.space_name, 
    COUNT(be.blocked_id) as fixed_extensions_count 
FROM space s 
LEFT JOIN blocked_extension be ON s.space_id = be.space_id AND be.is_fixed = true AND be.is_deleted = false 
WHERE s.is_deleted = false 
GROUP BY s.space_id, s.space_name 
ORDER BY s.space_id;
")

Bash(docker exec backend-postgres-1 psql -U postgres -d file_extension_blocker -c "
SELECT space_id, extension, is_fixed 
FROM blocked_extension 
WHERE space_id = 1 AND is_fixed = true 
ORDER BY extension;
")
Bash(docker exec backend-postgres-1 psql -U postgres -d file_extension_blocker -c "SELECT space_id, extension, is_fixed FROM blocked_extension WHERE is_fixed = false ORDER BY space_id, extension;")

Bash(docker exec backend-postgres-1 psql -U postgres -d file_extension_blocker -c "SELECT extension, COUNT(*) as cnt FROM blocked_extension WHERE is_deleted = false GROUP BY extension ORDER BY cnt DESC LIMIT 6;")
